{"tid":2492040,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人眼角久唔久就會閃一閃?","createTime":"2021-04-16T18:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T20:30:43.000Z","uid":229397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c8df18a1755daf689b51633492ad44364470fcc","tid":2492040,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:55:16.000Z","msg":"前幾日開始隻右眼久唔久就會閃一閃, 大約1小時1~3次, 冇飛蚊。視力正常, 亦冇對眼做過任何特別嘢, 極少摔眼。好少用電話打機, 通常睇片但電話光暗通常都係20%以下而且長開護眼mode。<br />\n究竟係咩事?"},{"pid":"1ae1a58e00d0875877d32e7d79157ad63f5ffa9d","tid":2492040,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:59:40.000Z","msg":"留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5edbc879a3c57dc7b563bcdb2ba4ad4b11b9366","tid":2492040,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:01:13.000Z","msg":"有時會<br />\n留明"},{"pid":"f0f627943ba6340c05bac08944c2ab1b29de3141","tid":2492040,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:01:45.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 睇普通科門診先<br />\n見你後生通常快期refer你去公院眼科<br />\n唔好google自己嚇自己<br />\n冇病都變有病"},{"pid":"79a79af189af7faec018e4677f21a9d617d4ff3b","tid":2492040,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:03:05.000Z","msg":"淨係隻右眼, 右眼既右上角眼尾咁上下位置。<br />\n閃得唔係好光, 閃一閃就完, 冇持續時間。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dda47fa184a5dd55c07c424078019335c807798","tid":2492040,"uid":378672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"視網膜問題 ，你有深近視？ 撞過個頭？<br />\n<br />\n即刻搵學位optometrist（驗眼師） 或眼科醫生睇眼底 （Retina）"},{"pid":"83e9e816045a7efa5b0c6194900bd310d11c6b88","tid":2492040,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0f627943ba6340c05bac08944c2ab1b29de3141","tid":2492040,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:01:45.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 睇普通科門診先<br />\n見你後生通常快期refer你去公院眼科<br />\n唔好google自己嚇自己<br />\n冇病都變有病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:06:10.000Z","msg":"就係goole過, 話會視網膜脫落。我明人係好化學, 但唔多覺/明會咁嚴重。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係正常現象? <br />\n只係3X中佬一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7600e14120c96f29ce794f5ae09392cf5f2e685","tid":2492040,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dda47fa184a5dd55c07c424078019335c807798","tid":2492040,"uid":378672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"視網膜問題 ，你有深近視？ 撞過個頭？<br />\n<br />\n即刻搵學位optometrist（驗眼師） 或眼科醫生睇眼底 （Retina）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"冇, 由細到大都唔洗戴眼鏡。幾年前陪EX配眼鏡, 屎忽痕check過, 遠近散光都係100內咁上下, 總知就係唔洗戴眼鏡既度數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇嘢清楚, 亦冇撞過頭/眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4f198b706ca36cd493c109dd5eb92064ad3097","tid":2492040,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T20:30:43.000Z","msg":"試過，玩得手機耐，而家限定最多連續3粒鍾就熄機"}]}